examples.en: He was traded to the Yankees.

examples.en: The Yankees scored 3 runs in the bottom of the 9th.

examples.en: It'll be the Red Sox vs. the Yankees in tonight's game.
examples.ru: В сегодняшнем матче "Бостон Ред Сокс" будут играть с "Нью-Йорк Янкиз".

examples.en: The Yankees played a three-game series against the Red Sox last week.
